        "content": "<p><span class=\"user-mention silent\" data-user-id=\"724904\">rzeta0</span> <a href=\"#narrow/stream/113489-new-members/topic/struggling.20to.20find.20maths.20strategy.20to.20show.20inequality/near/470367373\">said</a>:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>My interpretation of this is: Find an example of <code>a</code> such that <em>for all</em> <code>n : ℤ</code> the condition <code>2*a^3 ≥ n*a + 7</code> holds. Tell me if my interpretation is wrong.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>The order of the quantifier is wrong here. For all <code>n</code> you have to provide some <code>a</code> which satisfies the condition, so <code>a</code> is allowed to depend on <code>n</code>.</p>",
